programme.desc: Cikgu Thiya, anak hartawan yang memilih dunia pendidikan berbanding kemewahan. Tanggungjawab mengurus kutipan dana sekolah mempertemukannya dengan Tengku Faal, pewaris syarikat hartanah yang keras kepala. programme.title: World Watch: Africa’s Hunter Ep7
programme.desc: Ikuti kehidupan pemangsa hebat di Zambia seperti singa, harimau bintang dan hyena, yang bersaing dalam dunia liar yang semakin mencabar. Pelbagai perubahan berlaku dari kelahiran impala serentak hingga kemunculan makhluk ganjil seperti anai-anai terbang. Alam liar Lembah ini bersedia menghadapi musim baharu. Episod kali ini mengenai Hyena berbintik yang muda adalah anak betina alpha yang mengetuai pasukan hyena Lembah Luangwa. Apabila dewasa mereka akan meninggalkan kumpulan mereka dan pergi secara bersendirian.

programme.title: Bidadari: Kerana Hafsanya Setia Ep24
programme.desc: Segalanya seakan sempurna apabila Delaila dan Ali Syukri disatukan atas dasar cinta. Tapi benarlah kata orang, kahwin pada usia muda itu banyak cabarannya. Bahtera rumah tangga mereka diuji dengan kehadiran orang ketiga dan Delaila membawa diri ke New York. Dua belas tahun kemudian, pertemuan di New York telah membuka semula kisah mereka. Hud telah meluahkan perasaannya pada Delilah tapi dia terima takdir jika Delilah bukan jodohnya. Wairah sudah tahu wanita yang Hud suka adalah Delilah. Hud tahu mengenai Ali adalah bekas suami Delilah. Wairah telah memberitahu pada Hud tentang Delilah yang merosakkan rumah tangganya dan hubungannya dengan Ali. Delilah pulang ke kampung dan menerima lamaran Ali. Keluarga Delilah menerima segala keputusannya. Pelakon: Azrel Ismail, Mona Ellen, Octovia Menrose dan Daler Yusuf.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: 3S Serba Serbi Servis Ep1
programme.desc: Drama sitkom ini memaparkan perjalanan syarikat 3 S (Serba Serbi Servis) milik Datuk J yang menyediakan perkhidmatan penyelenggaraan di sebuah pangsapuri. Pelbagai telatah lucu dan aksi spontan berlaku dalam urusan seharian mereka dengan para penduduk di pangsapuri tersebut. Episod kali ini mengisahkan Roi menyedari harga di kedai Muthu semakin meningkat sehingga menyebabkan dia mula berhutang sewaktu membeli makanan. Dalam waktu yang sama, Remy telah menunjukkan bil air rumah Roi yang semakin bertambah akibat tidak dibayar. Ini menyebabkan bekalan air di rumahnya telah dipotong.

programme.title: Spektra: Derhaka Cinta Jebat Ep16
programme.desc: Semua berpunca kerana rasa dendam, salah faham dan ditambah pula dengan ego yang tinggi melangit, sanggup Jebat Zulkarnain menzalimi Aisyah Humaira isterinya sendiri. Bijaknya Jebat mengatur rancangan agar Aisyah jatuh cinta padanya hingga membawa kepada sebuah perkahwinan dengan niat ingin membalas dendam. Aisyah Humaira, suatu ketika dahulu pernah menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan adik lelaki Jebat, iaitu Tuah Iskandar. Tanpa usul periksa Jebat menjatuhkan hukuman tanpa memberi peluang kepada Aisyah untuk menjelaskan segala-galanya. Aisyah dituduh berlaku curang dengan Tuah dan menjadi penyebab musibah yang menimpa adik lelaki kesayangannya. Aisyah benar-benar kecewa. Jebat mendustai cintanya. Dia dinikahi Jebat bukan untuk disayang, dicintai sepenuh hati tapi Jebat punya agendanya sendiri. Misi Jebat hanyalah satu, melunaskan dendamnya dan membalas balik segala kesengsaraan Tuah yang kononnya dikhianati Aisyah dahulu. Pelakon: Elvina Mohamad, Azlee Khairi, Ikmal Amry, Mimi Ernida, Nina Fazurina, Wilma Muhammad dan Aznah Hamid.

programme.title: Kelana Pulau Ep8
programme.desc: Majalah travelog yang memaparkan keistimewaan tempat menarik yang dikunjungi oleh Mona Allen dan Anna Dahlia dari pelbagai aspek seperti kebudayaan, makanan dan aktiviti menarik yang terdapat di tempat tersebut. Bersama Mona dan Ana menjelajah bagi menyelesaikan misi melalui petunjuk yang mereka terima. Episod kali ini Ana akan berseorangan ke Pulau Perhentian Besar dan seterusnya ditemani Mona untuk ke Temerloh, Pahang. Saksikan tempat menarik seperti Pusat Konservasi Gajah, Kuala Gandah dan makanan terkenal di Temerloh iaitu Gulai Ikan Patin Tempoyak.

programme.title: Setia Menunggumu Ep13
programme.desc: Rahman masih terkejut, dia memberitahu bahawa Adi adalah anaknya dengan bukti dokumen yang ditunjukkan oleh Adi itu. Lalu Rahman membawa Adi berjumpa dengan Zainab (mak kandung Adi). Mereka menyuruh Adi tinggal bersama dengan mereka, tetapi Adi memilih untuk tinggal di madrasah sahaja. Sekali sekala Zainab menyuruh Sakinah menjemput Adi untuk datang ke rumah mereka, Rahman dan Zainab mahu memberikan apa sahaja untuk Adi kerana dia telah meninggalkan Adi hampir 20 tahun. Zainab dan Rahman mahu jodohkan Adi dengan Sakinah.

Pembuatannya yang rumit dan mencabar memerlukan kepakaran yang tinggi untuk mengendalikan asap yang tebal dan haba yang sangat panas yang dikawal selama 24 jam. programme.title: Araf 6
programme.desc: Yavuz, yang telah berpisah dengan isterinya Aye, ialah seorang guru kelas yang menjalani kehidupan biasa antara sekolah dan rumah. Kehidupan Yavuz berubah sama sekali apabila seorang pelajar perempuan bernama Amber masuk ke dalam kelasnya, seorang gadis yang tidak pernah berbicara dengan sesiapa. Sehari sebelum Amber hadir ke sekolah, Yavuz sebenarnya telah melihatnya di dalam mimpinya.

programme.desc: Black menolong Sofia menyelamatkan seseorang yang rapat dengan Sofia tapi itu hanya menyebabkan mereka hampir maut. Semuanya tampak ada kaitan dengan runtuhan Pusat Membeli-Belah Seri Setia. Sementara itu, Aisya menerima tekanan daripada pembunuh upahan Si Jari Tengah untuk mencari pita video yang sukar ditemui - kegagalan yang akan membahayakan nyawa Malik. Siasatan Borhan mengejutkan dirinya apabila dia mendapati mangsa dalam kesnya adalah seseorang yang dia pernah kenal. Lokman kecewa apabila dia nampak abangnya sangat tamak mahu mengambil-alih Insurans Mahkota.

programme.title: Black S2 EP5 Ep5
programme.desc: Percubaan Black untuk menangkap 419 gagal akibat teleportasinya yang tidak berfungsi. Sementara itu, menggunakan fail kes ayahnya, Sofia menjejak pembunuh yang disyaki, hingga terjebak dalam situasi yang membahayakan nyawa. Aisya mendapati Black merahsiakan kebenaran penting daripada Sofia yang mengugat hubungan mereka. Borhan menyusul petunjuk yang membawanya kembali ke Seri Setia.

Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Black S2 EP5 Ep5
programme.desc: Percubaan Black untuk menangkap 419 gagal akibat teleportasinya yang tidak berfungsi. Sementara itu, menggunakan fail kes ayahnya, Sofia menjejak pembunuh yang disyaki, hingga terjebak dalam situasi yang membahayakan nyawa. Aisya mendapati Black merahsiakan kebenaran penting daripada Sofia yang mengugat hubungan mereka. Borhan menyusul petunjuk yang membawanya kembali ke Seri Setia.

programme.title: 7 Seconds
programme.desc: Apabila seorang pencuri berpengalaman secara tidak sengaja melepaskan diri dengan Van Gogh, pasangannya diculik oleh samseng dalam mengejar lukisan itu, memaksa penjenayah itu untuk membuat rancangan menyelamat.

programme.title: Blood Vessel
programme.desc: Mangsa-mangsa yang terselamat menaiki sebuah bot Jerman yang dipenuhi dengan pontianak semasa Perang Dunia Kedua.

programme.title: Volkswagen Kuning
programme.desc: Filem ini diilhamkan oleh legenda urban terkenal Malaysia mengenai sebuah Volkswagen berwarna kuning yang misteri yang dilihat di Lebuhraya Karak. Mengikut legenda, apabila anda melihat kereta tersebut di lebuhraya, jangan sesekali memotongnya kerana kereta itu akan terus muncul di hadapan anda, dan yang lebih menakutkan, tiada pemandu yang dilihat mengemudi kereta tersebut.

programme.title: Araf 6
programme.desc: Yavuz, yang telah berpisah dengan isterinya Aye, ialah seorang guru kelas yang menjalani kehidupan biasa antara sekolah dan rumah. Kehidupan Yavuz berubah sama sekali apabila seorang pelajar perempuan bernama Amber masuk ke dalam kelasnya, seorang gadis yang tidak pernah berbicara dengan sesiapa. Sehari sebelum Amber hadir ke sekolah, Yavuz sebenarnya telah melihatnya di dalam mimpinya.

programme.title: Bohsia Jangan Pilih Jalan Hitam

programme.desc: Black berdepan dengan kes yang paling menggentarkan apabila emosinya terganggu buat pertama kali - seluruh skuad keluar mencari Bagas, yang juga dikenali sebagai Lelaki Berparut Cangkuk yang telah menahan dua orang tebusan, yang nampaknya cedera. programme.desc: Iklan dalam talian McCall membawanya kepada seorang ibu yang anaknya telah diculik oleh seorang pemerdagang manusia (Thomas Beaudoin) dan akan dibunuh melainkan dia mencuri maklumat sulit daripada majikannya, seorang ejen FBI. Selain itu, McCall meminta bantuan Aunt Vi untuk membongkar rahsia yang sedang disembunyikan oleh Delilah daripada mereka berdua.

programme.desc: Percutian keluarga berubah menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila mereka berdepan dengan seekor jerung megalodon ganas. Terdampar dan diserang tanpa henti, Paul dan keluarganya mesti mencari jalan untuk kembali ke pantai dengan selamat sebelum jerung itu menyerang lagi.

Kawan sejuk milien, pemandu teksi Daniel Morales, pada mulanya hanya bersetuju untuk menjaga anak-anak lelaki kawan mereka, kerana isteri milien, Petra, sedang menjalankan misi rahsia. Tetapi tidak lama kemudian, penjenayah Belgium itu melarikan diri, dan semasa mengejarnya, rakan-rakan itu tersandung pada satu perampokan bank dan sebuah vila megah milik raja dadah, di mana babak akhir yang hebat berlaku.

programme.title: Dia Ibuku
programme.desc: Rohani perlu bekerja keras untuk menyara anak-anaknya, Jamal dan Jamil kerana statusnya sebagai seorang janda. Perjumpaan itu membawa kembali kenangan silam yang pahit.

programme.title: Bintang Malam
programme.desc: Selepas dua belas tahun berlayar, Yazid dan Johari akhirnya pulang semula ke tanah air. Yazid pula keluar mencari Aisah di bandar - tetapi berdepan dengan pelbagai konflik dan tragedi.

programme.title: Leftenan Adnan
programme.desc: Adnan memutuskan untuk menjadi seorang tentera dalam pasukan Askar Melayu setelah dikunjungi anggota tentera British yang datang ke kampungnya untuk merekrut lebih ramai anak tempatan. Tidak direstui keluarga, Adnan nekad untuk mengikuti latihan ketenteraan di Port Dickson. programme.desc: Rumahtangga Amir dan Asmah berubah setelah mereka didatangi seorang pembantu rumah misteri yang membantu mendapatkan mereka cahaya mata. Selepas melahirkan anak dalam tempoh yang singkat, satu demi satu insiden aneh menimpa ahli keluarga dan kenalan mereka.

programme.title: Matinya Seorang Patriot
programme.desc: Pengerusi Melati Holdings, Haji Saaban meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba yang menimbulkan keraguan tentang kematiannya. Safuan mengesyaki bahawa kematian bapanya ada kena mengena dengan syarikat bapanya. Saiful yang pada mulanya ingin membalas dendam kematian bapanya mula berubah apabila jatuh cinta dengan anak kepada ahli lembaga pengarah. Safuan menganggap Saiful telah mengkhianati keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Aku Yang Berhormat
programme.desc: Seorang petani dan anggota sukarelawan, Hamid dan Jaafar ingin menjatuhkan Jamali - wakil rakyat yang tidak telus dan kejam. Mereka berdua berusaha mendapatkan sokongan orang kampung supaya dapat menaikkan Hamid sebagai wakil rakyat baharu sekaligus menggantikan Jamali. Dharma dan Rosnah turut terpalit dengan kisah percintaan. Orang-orang kampung juga disarankan untuk menyimpan di Amanah Saham Nasional buat masa hadapan mereka di dalam kisah ini.

programme.title: Ringgit Kasorrga
programme.desc: Kekayaan, kemewahan dan hawa nafsu - semuanya boleh didapati di Pulau Kasorrga. Pulau khas buat warga elit ini menjadi tempat buat orang kaya untuk mencari ketenangan dan kepuasan. Pemilik syarikat permodelan dan pencari bakat, Meera Almeida membekalkan gadis ke pulau itu dan dibayar wang komisen yang tinggi. Namun rahsia gelap Pulau Kasorrga mula diungkai sedikit demi sedikit.

programme.title: Leftenan Adnan
programme.desc: Adnan memutuskan untuk menjadi seorang tentera dalam pasukan Askar Melayu setelah dikunjungi anggota tentera British yang datang ke kampungnya untuk merekrut lebih ramai anak tempatan. Tidak direstui keluarga, Adnan nekad untuk mengikuti latihan ketenteraan di Port Dickson. Perjuangan Leftenan Adnan dalam mempertahankan Tanah Melayu memberikan inspirasi kepada ramai anak muda tempatan.

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: Cesium Fallout
programme.desc: A massive fire caused by illegal garbage smuggling has triggered a radiation crisis in Hong Kong. Government advisor Simon joins the crisis response team led by Acting Chief Executive to avert the disaster. A fire brigade is tasked to enter the radiation zone and stop the cesium fallout. Facing the unprecedented catastrophe, can they save the city?

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Set in 2020 during the outbreak of COVID-19, the movie features interconnected stories of three women's lives as they navigate the uncertain future amongst their respective friends and families. From the struggles at home to challenges in relationships and conflicts at work, these three women rise with strength when faced with plights unknown.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. The younger brother is a drug lord while the elder brother Zhong is a police officer in the Narcotics Bureau. Both are involved in a drug cartels turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brothers hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: Ha Ha Ha Happy New Year!!
programme.desc: Business tycoon Duan is kidnapped and seriously injured by the "Shadow Empire", accidentally losing his memory. Duan is looked after by Su, a temple owner, and as he slowly recovers, Duan discovers that he has been replaced by a doppelgnger, prompting him to uncover a shocking hidden secret.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult: Ultimate Malevolence
programme.desc: The final chapter of 'Tales From The Occult', the movie features three short stories about two high school friends, a magician undergoing hypnosis to find her missing friend, and a man finding his way out of a mysterious building. The stories reveal the most terrifying and ugly side of human nature, where life and death are just a thought away!

programme.title: Love is the only Answer
programme.desc: At Bo and Cheong wedding reception, the projected was initially showing their journey of love, but suddenly a flash of a clip of Cheong and a sexy girl being intimate came up. Bo calmly ran up to the stage and announced that the wedding is cancelled. The incident rapidly became a hot topic on the internet. Within a year, back to being single again, Bo and the living life happily Cheong maintains a good relationship. One day, Cheong decided to play with love and took Bo to participate in a swinging party. The conservative Bo initially wanted to leave, but after being bribed by Cheong, she helpless and stayed. At the swinging party, the two encounter Kit and his wife Man Lai. The 4 of them develop a romantic and hot relationship... At another wedding reception, when the projector plays the groom and bride's heartwarming clips, a flash of another clip that does not want to be seen comes up...

programme.title: Dummy Mommy, without a Baby
programme.desc: Fong Lai Kuen works at an advertising agency but is about to be sacked by her boss after offending him. She pretends to be pregnant so that the company cannot fire her, according to the labour law. Since then, Fong receives much care and love from her colleagues and begins to feel guilty about her lie as things develop out of her expectations.

programme.title: Born to Fly
programme.desc: Lei Yu has officially become the new generation of Chinese test pilots after rounds of strict selection. Captain Zhang Ting leads Lei Yu and other pilots to test the latest fighter jets. Lei Yu keeps pushing the limits in each test flight in the hope of coming up with the perfect plane to ensure the safety of the fighter pilots.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Love For All Seasons
programme.desc: May, acting leader of the Er Mei sect, cures the incurable illness of Tiger, a rich playboy. Under the threat of her senior, May seeks help from Tiger to experience heartbreak and master the "Heartbroken Sword" style, so as to defeat her senior and preserve Er Mei sect. Will this strange and long-winding relationship reach a happy ending?

programme.title: Ha Ha Ha Happy New Year!!
programme.desc: Business tycoon Duan is kidnapped and seriously injured by the "Shadow Empire", accidentally losing his memory. Duan is looked after by Su, a temple owner, and as he slowly recovers, Duan discovers that he has been replaced by a doppelgnger, prompting him to uncover a shocking hidden secret.

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: Crypto Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigation officer Lok sets up a special team to investigate a corruption case involving a banks top executives use of cryptocurrency to manipulate the trading market. When the banks chairman is kidnapped and kidnappers demand ransom in crypto coins, Lok connects the dots and vows to hunt down the mastermind behind both crimes.

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: Love Lies
programme.desc: Gynaecologist Veronica downloads a dating app for fun. Little does she know that the charming French engineer on the other end is actually a local con artist named Joe, who is a member of an online scam group. As their fake relationship unfolds, both Joes guilty conscience and Veronicas hopes intensify.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighbouring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: As It Burns
programme.desc: Detective Wei investigates the death of Yan Zhen in an explosion which seems more than an accident to him. Wei then finds out that Yan Zhen looks a lot like Yin, the girlfriend of Yan Zhens childhood friend Lu, and uncovers a tangled web of deceit leading to surprising revelations when he merges details from the past and the present.

programme.title: Love Punch
programme.desc: Talented boxer Jia Yang is caught in an underground fight to clear her father's debts. She loses her Olympic aspiration and vanishes from the boxing world. 10 years later, Coach Li Yue is determined to help her honour her father's wish by returning to the ring. As passion and obligation collide, can Jia Yang revive her abandoned boxing dream?

programme.title: HK Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her teams performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night. Lee runs into her ex-boyfriend before a big commercial shoot and drowns her sorrows drinking at Lan Kwai Fong, but finally picks herself up with Chans help.

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: Confinement
programme.desc: Si Ling, a pregnant painter, moves into her dream home after winning an award and hires a confinement nanny. As she begins her one-month confinement after giving birth to her daughter, inexplicable incidents start happening in the house, threatening both her and her baby

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killers mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened

programme.title: WE12
programme.desc: An underground organization, The League of Kaito has been maintaining international order. While 12 elite members possess extraordinary skills and have worked independently for a period of time, they must rekindle their long-lost team spirit to accomplish a mission together to save the world from disaster.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the Gang of Five in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: Bangkok Storm
programme.desc: Underground boxer Lin Feng is hunted by the Bangkok triad when he refuses to fight in an illegal match. He escaped successfully but lost his memory. While Feng begins a new life, the triad finds him and hires a top boxer to beat him. As Feng suddenly regains his memory in the process, he vows to take down the triad.

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong 2013
programme.desc: Sung Chi Hung and Ha Shek Lam worked at a Chinese restaurant when they were young and both fell in love with the owners daughter, Yeung. Sung and Yeung eventually got married and took over the restaurant. Many years later, Sung meets Ha who is now a real estate tycoon and plans to buy out the restaurant. Can Sung save the restaurant?

programme.title: One More Chance
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as a down-on-his-luck gambler, Water, whose ex-girlfriend asked him to take care of their autistic son. As Water lives with his son, he soon finds his goal in life. When he discovers his sons talent in running, Water decides to give up his dissipated life and support his son to achieve his dream.

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: A titular gang of misfits come together to protect a patriotic general from a scheming usurper. To this end, the unlikely heroes act as the general's escorts on a dangerous journey to a distant British consulate, beset by enemies and sinister Japanese interference along the way.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: Shadow Girl
programme.desc: A young swordswoman becomes invisible during the day and a monster at night after taking her grandma's pill. She ruined the wedding of a bandit chief's daughter using her powers and is hunted down by them for revenge. Will she escape the hunt?

programme.title: King Drummer
programme.desc: A young musician Chi Chiang is hired by the manager of a popular band when the group's drummer/leader Charlie, quits to join a rival group. The new drummer becomes an immediate hit, causing Charlie to be very jealous. Furthermore, the young drummer's mother is dead set against him having a music career.

programme.title: That Man In Chang-An
programme.desc: The Han Emperor dies and his Empress Lu seizes the ruling power. She plots to kill the heir to the throne, Liu Heng, but the masked warrior discovers her plot and tips off Liu. Liu sends his princess to Chang An to ask for help. The masked warrior protects the princess from attackers along the way and supports Liu to become the new Emperor.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70's Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sister's magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wong's disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his bride use the deadly weapon - Phoenix Lute to fight against evil, but the lute accidentally falls into the hands of bandits hoping to use it to take control of the province. Gui Wu must now fight to recover the lute and beat the bandits.

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Purple Darts
programme.desc: A girl vows to take revenge for her parents who were murdered by four outlaws when she was only a baby. To do so, she trains hard at martial arts and teams up with a swordsman and a couple to finally kill them all.

programme.title: The Fastest Sword
programme.desc: Southern Swordsman Ting is named The Fastest Sword but is defeated by a street monk and has to fulfil his promise of working on stone craving with the monk for three years. Ting returns home to lead a peaceful life after that and declines all fight challenges. Even so, he is forced to fight the Northern Swordsman. Who will win finally?

programme.title: Whose Baby Is In The Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls' high school, is stuck with a baby that isn't his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: Two Champions Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Set in the Qing Dynasty, the Shaolin clan wants to overthrow Qing and restore the Ming Dynasty, while the Wudang clan is backed by the Qing government. The two renowned clans eventually set themselves up against each other, and a series of vicious fighting has just begun

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: The Kid With A Tattoo
programme.desc: Young Bao Tong witnesses the brutal murder of his kung fu master by a vicious villain. A large eagle tattoo on Bao's chest was spotted by the killer as he escapes. Can Bao escape from the killer?

programme.title: Tragic Commitment
programme.desc: When the husband of a doctor, Tung is fatally wounded in an accident, he reveals to her about his affair with Blackie, who is impregnated with his baby. Despite the devastation of the betrayal and the eventual death of her husband, Tung is pressured by her mother-in-law into putting up with Blackie and offer $1M for her baby...

programme.title: The Killer Has No Return
programme.desc: Professional killer Lui goes to Malaysia after completing his mission of killing the big boss of a Hong Kong gang. His next target is a groom who is throwing his wedding banquet at a hotel in Chinatown. Just when Lui takes aim at his target, another victim instead of the groom is shot, and he becomes a scapegoat in this mystery assassination.

programme.title: The Emperor And The Minister
programme.desc: The ingenious imperial scholar Liu Yung always embarrasses Emperor Chien Lung with his quick wit and gift of gab. The emperor purposely sets him up to solve the seemingly unsolvable. However, Liu Yung resolves it easily with wit and style and foils the emperor's plot once again.

programme.title: The Dragon Creek
programme.desc: This wuxia murder mystery film talks about a young girl whose father was ruthlessly murdered during China's early republican era. She has a list of villains who have been plotting against her father and together with her elder brother, the young girl sets out on a journey to hunt down the secret serial killer.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Long's wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: Brothers From The Walled City
programme.desc: Two orphaned brothers growing up in Kowloon's Walled City - the place where people are forced to live with indecent businesses of sex, gambling and drugs controlled by triads - take very different life paths. Chin works at a cabaret but keeps away from sins, while Kang is drawn to the sleazy underworld. Are their destinies shaped by the walls?

programme.title: Mr Funny - Bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: The Reckless Cricket
programme.desc: Inspired by Drunken Master, this kung fu comedy features a bumbling martial artist creating a cricket-style fighting arts to fight and defeat the different martial artists who have beaten him before.

programme.title: Disciples Of The 36th Chamber
programme.desc: In the finale of this trilogy, Gordon Liu reprises his famous role, Monk San Te, as he tries to protect Fang Shih Yu, an arrogant youth who gets into trouble with the Qing officials, and nearly lands Shaolin Temple into trouble too.

programme.title: Love Without End
programme.desc: Singer Qing Qing and architect Peng Nan are a devoted couple. Qing Qing sacrifices herself to help Peng Nan when his family is going through difficulties and is misunderstood by Peng Nan, leading to their break up. When Peng Nan learns the truth and decides to make up with Qing Qing, he finds out that she is suffering from a terminal illness.

programme.title: The Spirit Of The Sword
programme.desc: Water Clan Chief is severely wounded by a samurai killer shortly before the annual duel at Tai Lake. He sends his brother Bao Yu on a long journey to find an antidote for him. On the way, Bao Yu encounters Little Princess and falls in love with her, not knowing that she is hiding a secret plot

programme.title: The Mirror And The Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: Usurpers Of Emperor'S Power
programme.desc: The last ruler of Tang, Li Yao is deposed by Chao Kuang-jun, the founder of the Sung Dynasty. Unfortunately his actions unleash a new plague - his brother Kuang-yi - on the courts and his people. The marauding Kuang-yi rapes and plunders. As more people get involved, it turns into a bloody battlefield of betrayal. It is up to upright officials like Li Lang to put an end to it. But can one man take on the imperial army?

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: Martial Club
programme.desc: The young Wong Fei Hung and his friend Wang Yin Lin offend the young master of another rival school and the expert they hire, causing both martial arts schools to fight against each other. This is Director Liu Chia Liang's masterpiece and one of the top ten highest grossing movies in 1981.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: Opium And The Kung-Fu Master
programme.desc: Tie Qiao San, head of the Ten Guangdong Tigers, is an honourable master with many disciples. As opium becomes popular among the nobles, Tie starts taking it and gradually harms his body. When an opium house's owner defeats Tie in a fight and he is only saved from being killed by his disciple, Tie vows to quit opium and get back on his feet.

programme.title: Melody Of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s a-go-go era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: The Jade Raksha
programme.desc: A fearsome swordswoman known as The Jade Raksha appears in the martial arts world and begins killing people whose surname is Yan. A swordsman figures out who she is and asks her why. Apparently a Yan killed her family 18 years ago and she only has vengeance on her mind
